  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Beams and Fighters</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>A somewhat small avian race with gray or dark plumag=
e and
  a striking physical presence.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>They are an aggressive species but often uses quick =
action
  to scare others and try and gain advantage.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Long ago, the <span class=3DSpellE>Ylta</span> descr=
ibe a
  time when they were a race consumed by greed. They labored, betrayed other
  species at will and fought wars over material wealth, thinking the
  acquisition of goods was the sole path to spiritual ascension.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Eventually they were completely defeated by their
  accumulated enemies. The <span class=3DSpellE>Ylta</span> describe this as
  their Time of Shadow, as their planet fell under centuries of anarchy and
  scattered recorded history.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Ylta</span> describe a time=
 of
  eventual Spiritual awakening, where they were gifted tools of creation and
  untold power that quickly propelled them back to the stars.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Ylta</span> now seek to kno=
w the
  Galaxy, its wonders and what rarities it hides. Despite the empire's goals
  and recent change in ethos, its people's happiness and productivity are s=
till
  largely affected by the wealth the Yl'ta has access to.</p>
